SUMMARY:Blood on the Clocktower at Blue Note
DESCRIPTION:Yolo County Board Game Gathering\nThe first Wednesday of every
  month\, we play _Blood on the Clocktower_\, a social deduction game in th
 e vein of Werewolf/Mafia/The Resistance\, with a few twists!\n\nWe'll have
  a circle of chairs reserved inside Blue Note\, near the back\, with a Yol
 o County Board Game Gathering sign on the table. Just say hello\, and we'l
 l show you some games\, pull some players together\, and get to having fun
 !\n\nWe also usually have a few tables of players playing other board game
 s\, if social deduction isn't your bag!\n\nGet a feel for Blood on the Clo
 cktower here: https://youtu.be/4sfa8_kNxsQ
