SUMMARY:Lake Berryessa Electric Boat Festival
DESCRIPTION:Just minutes from Winters\, the Lake Berryessa Electric Boat Festival at Pleasure Cove Marina is a one-of-a-kind event and the ‘World’s Largest Electric Boat Experience’ where clean technology\, outdoor adventure\, and wine country lifestyle come together.\n​ \nSpend the day on the water exploring the next generation of electric boats\, meeting innovators shaping the future of marine technology\, and enjoying a curated waterfront experience featuring artisan wineries\, olive oil producers\, local cheese makers\, and lifestyle exhibitors. \n​What You’ll Experience\n​• Ride and demo close to 15 of the most advanced electric boats on the market\n• Kayak and electric propulsion systems\n• Learn about the future of marina electrification\n• Explore new electric watercraft and marine innovation \nTo purchase tickets\, click here.
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/lake-berryessa-electric-boat-festival/
LOCATION:Pleasure Cove Marina\, 6100 CA-128\, Napa\, 94558\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/6aec65c3-440f-470b-b004-5735b6cab0e1-1-copy.jpeg
ORGANIZER;CN="Charged Marine":MAILTO:info@chargedmarine.com
END:VEVENT
