SUMMARY:Davis PrideFest
DESCRIPTION:Discover the heart and spirit of our vibrant community at Davis Pride. Davis Pride is more than just a party; we are Yolo County’s largest LGBTQ+ advocacy event. We encourage you to come and explore everything Davis Pride has to offer. \nThe 12th annual Davis Pride will bring a month of events to celebrate and support the local\nLGBTQ+ community\, with Davis PrideFest\, a fun run\, trivia\, and the annual comedy night.\nThe month-long celebration will start with PrideFest\, taking place at Civic Center Park\, at 6th\nand B streets behind Davis City Hall\, from 4:00 to 9:00 p.m. on Saturday\, June 6. This family-\nfriendly event features a music festival\, community vendors\, food trucks\, drinks\, and a drag\nrevue.
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/davis-pridefest/
LOCATION:Davis Civic Center Park\, 6th and B Streets\, Davis\, 95616\, United States
ORGANIZER;CN="The Davis Phoenix Coalition":MAILTO:admin@davisphoenixco.org
END:VEVENT
